metadata.name: VaultBooster #1
metadata.description: The VaultBooster is essentially a booster for the ETHVault NFT. This booster includes benefits such as automatic WL to the main mint, greater ETHScore, a more favorable ETHScore Equation, greater $EVLT yield, marketplace discounts and much more! A full list of benefits for the VaultBooster can be found on Discord. You must own a ETHVault NFT to be able to use the utility of this boost
